OL,3,CResidents angry at 'river' of sewage
OL,4,Cwater outside their homes
OL,6,FA family in Eastbourne say their lives
OL,7,Fare being made a misery by a 'river'
OL,8,Fof sewage surging from a manhole cover
OL,9,Foutside their home.
OL,11,FLouise and Lee Bridgwater, who live in
OL,12,FWartling Road, say that it prevents
OL,13,Fthem from leaving their house
OL,14,Fsometimes.
OL,16,FThe couple say they've strengthened
OL,17,Ftheir garden wall to protect it
OL,18,Fagainst the pressure of water leaving
OL,19,Fthe drain and built a flood barrier to
OL,20,Fprevent it coming down the drive.
