OL,3,CResidents angry at 'river' of sewage
OL,4,Cwater outside their homes
OL,6,F"We have had to strengthen our garden
OL,7,Fwall to protect it against the
OL,8,Fpressure of the water leaving the
OL,9,Fdrain. We have built a flood barrier
OL,10,Fto prevent the water coming down our
OL,11,Fdrive - which is the only thing
OL,12,Fpreventing our home from being
OL,13,Fcompletely flooded.
OL,15,F"We have installed air brick covers,
OL,16,Fshould they be needed. We have to keep
OL,17,Faware of predicted rainfall to
OL,18,Fdetermine if we need to put the flood
OL,19,Fbarrier out and be prepared for
OL,20,Fflooding."
