OL,3,CResidents angry at 'river' of sewage
OL,4,Cwater outside their homes
OL,6,FAround the corner in Rye Street is
OL,7,Fwhere the sewage water collects,
OL,8,Faccording to residents.
OL,10,FThey say the water reaches car door
OL,11,Fheight, flooding into their cars, as
OL,12,Fwell as going up their paths.
OL,14,FAlex Saunders, Southern Water's Head
OL,15,Fof Wastewater Networks, said: "We are
OL,16,Fsorry that our customers are
OL,17,Fexperiencing these issues.
OL,19,F"Our teams are doing everything they
OL,20,Fcan to resolve them as quickly as
OL,21,Fpossible.
