OL,6,F"Unfortunately, the cause of this
OL,7,Fflooding is complex. We have carried
OL,8,Fout extensive investigations already,
OL,9,Fand these are continuing ` with our
OL,10,Fteams due to visit the area again in
OL,11,Fthe coming days.
OL,13,F"We will keep all local customers
OL,14,Fupdated as we search for a sustainable
OL,15,Flong-term solution."
